heading: Tambura (Fretted lute) ensembles.
general-note: Here are entered compositions not in a specific form or of a specific type for ten or more solo fretted lute tamburas and collections of compositions in several forms or types for various numbers of solo fretted lute tamburas..
When used for an accompanying ensemble in headings, the term "tambura (Fretted lute) ensemble" stands for two or more solo fretted lute tamburas..
